42

regard  to  those  procedures,  they  need  to  be  worked  out  before  we
can fully commit—before I could responsibly commit to you that we
should  undertake  the  servicing  mission.  What  I  have  said  in  prior
testimony and in public remarks is that by this fall, when we have
completed  those  two  missions,  we  will  know  those  answers.  And  if
those  answers  are  favorable,  then  I  will  recommend  that  we  exe-
